<item>
            <title>[FLINK-996] NullPointerException while translating union node</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-996</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The NepheleJobGraphGenerator throws a NullPointerException when translating a binary union operator. The BinaryUnionPlanNode is not replaced by a NAryUnionPlanNode and thus is still treated as a DualInputVertex. Accessing the driver code of the BinaryUnionPlanNode causes then the NullPointerException.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12724922">FLINK-996</key>
            <summary>NullPointerException while translating union node</summary>
